        <p><b>Here is what we need:</b></p>

        <ul>
            <li>Reserve a slot by contacting <a href="https://twitter.com/Pixel_Robots" target="_blank">@@Pixel_Robots</a> or <a href="https://twitter.com/gregor_suttie" target="_blank">@@Gregor_suttie</a> on Twitter (with hash tag <a href="#">#azureadventcalendar</a>).</li>
            <li>Record a 20-30 minute video with an Azure topic</li>
            <li>Prepare a blog post (in English)</li>
            <li>Add a link in your blog post that links back to <a href="https://azureadventcalendar.com" target="_blank">azureadventcalendar.com</a>, so that your readers may find the entire azure advent calendar.
