            <li>Share your blog post on Twitter with hashtags <a href="#">#azurefamily</a> and <a href="#">#azureadventcalendar</a></li>
            <li>Any further questions contact <a href="https://twitter.com/Pixel_Robots" target="_blank">@@Pixel_Robots</a> or <a href="https://twitter.com/gregor_suttie" target="_blank">@@Gregor_suttie</a> on Twitter (with hash tag <a href="#">#azureadventcalendar</a>).</li>
            <li>Check out the faq's page <a href="https://azureadventcalendar.com/Home/FAQ" target="_blank">Azure Advent Calendar Faq's Page.</a> </li>
